=Description=

"Barcelona Maker Faire hosts the
most inspired, talented and ambitious
makers, enthusiastic to share all their
knowledge and creativity through
exhibitions, workshops, and
interactive demos.

With the participation of leading
international experts that will present
and discuss the latest results and
contributions in education, society,
and economics, Barcelona Maker
Faire wants to contribute promoting
imagination, creativity, innovation
and learning of new skills and ideas."

